casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
James HABEL, Defendant-Petitioner. C-297 September Term 2018
081170 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001473-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied without prejudice to defendant raising his challenges in a petition for post-conviction relief.
